    info\!(phase = 'setup', 'Creating test actors');
    // ... test code ...
    info\!(phase = 'verify', messages_sent = 10, 'Verifying message delivery');
}
```

### Required Log Fields
- `phase`: setup, execute, verify, teardown
- `actor_id`: When operating on specific actor
- `message_type`: Type of message being sent
